<figureCitation box="[826,916,609,634]" captionStart="FIGURES 40–54" captionStartId="12.[151,264,1837,1860]" captionTargetBox="[165,1425,353,1806]" captionTargetId="figure@12.[151,1435,339,1815]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="FIGURES 40–54. Anthaxia, pronotal sculpture (not in scale). 40—Anthaxia (Anthaxia) fulgurans (Schrank); 41—A. (A.) salicis salicis (Fabricius); 42—A. (A.) manca (Fabricius); 43—A. (Melanthaxia) nigrojubata nigrojubata Roubal; 44—A. (Cratomerus) hungarica hungarica (Scopoli); 45—A. (Haplanthaxia) cichorii (Olivier); 46—A. (H.) kneuckeri zabranskyi Bílý; 47—A. (H.) pumila (Klug); 48—A. (Richteraxia) angustipennis (Klug); 49—A. (R.) marginifera metallescens Bílý; 50— A. (Merocratus) tamdaoensis Bílý; 51—A. (Thailandia) rondoni Baudon; 52—A. (Capanthaxia) capensis Kerremans; 53—A. (Cap.) aterrima Kerremans; 54—A. (Cap.) sulcicollis Obenberger." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2599428/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="265">Fig. 40</figureCitation>
